00:40:01,800 --> 00:40:02,800
Mire.

625
00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:07,430
Si pone suficiente de esto...

626
00:40:07,520 --> 00:40:08,990
COMPUESTO: FLUNITRAZEPAM

627
00:40:09,080 --> 00:40:12,520
